# web/drive/viewer/ and web/drive/fzstd.js are populated by
# scripts/sync-drive-viewer.sh. We commit them (rather than generating
# on deploy) so a plain `firebase deploy` works without relying on
# predeploy hooks, and so cloning the repo gives a runnable PWA.
# Re-run scripts/sync-drive-viewer.sh after changing resources/viewer/
# or bumping the MapLibre / fzstd versions.
